[core] Increase margin to scroll

With 30px, it's often too close to the bottom of the screen,

Author: Olivier Tassinari
Commit Message:
[website] Fix broken career website links

See https://mui.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/7891, when we use relative links,
e.g. `[MUI Design kits](/design-kits/)` and we copy the rendered page from
our localhost to a new Ashby role, we then end up with broken links, e.g.
http://0.0.0.0:3000/careers/#perks-amp-benefits

So, instead, I'm forcing https://mui.com as a prefix. This impacts candidates
finding the role from Wellfound and from HNews.
